I doubt it.

32
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:19,800
Dad.

33
00:03:20,290 --> 00:03:22,330
- Slowly.
- Your mom is so bold!

34
00:03:23,170 --> 00:03:24,890
How could she get involved
in that thing?

35
00:03:27,130 --> 00:03:28,480
I was also foolish. I trusted her

36
