we lost our own money.

46
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,960
But what about others' money?

47
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,290
Do you know

48
00:03:53,290 --> 00:03:54,640
how much they invested?

49
00:03:56,410 --> 00:03:57,640
Mom said it wasn't much.

50
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,890
