56
00:04:22,530 --> 00:04:24,050
I don't want to worry her.

57
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,920
Finally, you came back to your senses.

58
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,440
That's great.

59
00:04:36,050 --> 00:04:36,920
The workload here

60
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,880
will keep you busy until the next life.

61
00:04:42,290 --> 00:04:43,320
From today on,

62
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,800
you will focus on designing.

63
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:48,050
We are the great duo.

64
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,240
Don't put me on a pedestal.

65
00:04:51,050 --> 00:04:52,440
Before that, I have to tell you this.

66
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,320
I won't resign from my job,

67
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,320
and I won't take a salary from you.

68
00:04:56,730 --> 00:04:57,650
