No problem.

77
00:05:11,530 --> 00:05:12,530
Tell me if you need money.

78
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,880
I'll definitely help you.

79
00:05:17,610 --> 00:05:19,320
It's fine, thanks.

80
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,680
I don't care.

81
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,290
You must work hard to earn for me.

82
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:24,240
Who is the expert

83
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,650
that works hard
to make money for you?

84
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:27,800
Wen Ya, perfect timing.

85
00:05:28,170 --> 00:05:29,410
You can meet Yu Jian,

86
00:05:29,410 --> 00:05:30,920
who you have been meaning to see.

87
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,850
He agreed to work in my humble studio.

88
00:05:33,410 --> 00:05:34,290
The level of this studio

89
00:05:34,290 --> 00:05:35,290
has been raised, right?

90
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,480
Look how happy you are.

91
00:05:37,730 --> 00:05:38,560
Here's your gift.

92
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,410
A gift?

93
00:05:42,290 --> 00:05:44,090
Yu Jian, it has been a while.

94
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,770
Yeah, Wen Ya.

95
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,360
Wen Ya,
are you going to say it yourself,

96
00:05:50,410 --> 00:05:51,480
or do you need my help?

97
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,530
Yu Jian isn't an outsider here.

98
00:05:53,730 --> 00:05:54,850
I will tell you right away.

99
00:05:55,410 --> 00:05:56,610
I want to open a flower shop.

100
00:05:56,970 --> 00:05:58,410
Not the ordinary one.

101
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,880
It's a cultural and creative

102
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,170
gift store with fresh flowers.

103
00:06:01,610 --> 00:06:02,480
Yiming said

104
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,440
you were coming today.

105
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,050
So, I rushed here.

106
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,290
I have brought the blueprint.

107
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,610
Could you design it

108
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,440
for me?

109
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,730
Just so you know,

110
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,770
Yu Jian

111
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,530
has strong opinions

112
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,560
and not anyone

113
00:06:17,730 --> 00:06:18,880
can make him change his mind.

114
00:06:19,410 --> 00:06:20,050
I think

115
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,240
you can discuss it first

116
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:23,120
before reaching the collaboration.

117
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,120
No need.

118
00:06:25,610 --> 00:06:26,320
I'm in.

119
00:06:26,730 --> 00:06:28,170
That's a fast answer.

120
00:06:29,530 --> 00:06:30,850
Wen Ya, did you cast a spell

121
00:06:30,970 --> 00:06:32,290
on Yu Jian?

122
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:34,410
That would be amazing.

123
00:06:34,770 --> 00:06:35,730
You know what?

124
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,680
When you decided not to go to Shanghai,

125
00:06:37,850 --> 00:06:39,290
she wanted me to keep an eye on you.

126
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,800
She asked me to replace Gao,
but I didn't agree.

127
00:06:42,170 --> 00:06:44,410
It's good now. She got her wish.

128
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,850
Yiming said

129
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,170
you are an all-rounder.

130
00:06:47,410 --> 00:06:49,650
You are good at every field.

131
00:06:50,410 --> 00:06:51,320
You are picky.

132
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:53,050
I can't guarantee if Yu Jian

133
00:06:53,170 --> 00:06:53,800
can fulfill

134
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,050
all your requests.

135
00:06:55,170 --> 00:06:56,850
It's like you are choosing
a boyfriend for me.

136
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:59,530
Of course, the guy must be perfect
in every way.

137
00:06:59,650 --> 00:07:01,240
Don't get any ideas about him.

138
00:07:01,770 --> 00:07:03,240
He's going to get married.

139
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,920
I know.

140
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:08,290
They are the most clingy couple
in Leshan.

141
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:10,850
I just have
a high standard of aesthetics.

142
00:07:11,090 --> 00:07:11,730
I'm sure

143
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:13,970
Yu Jian can manage that.

144
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,920
You are twisting my words around.

145
00:07:16,610 --> 00:07:17,780
Says who!

146
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:18,610
All right.

147
00:07:18,770 --> 00:07:19,530
Stop.

148
00:07:20,290 --> 00:07:22,050
Wen Ya, let's get back to business.

149
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:24,320
If you have any requests, ask away.

150
00:07:24,970 --> 00:07:25,650
There is no rush.

151
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,290
Let's have dinner together.

152
00:07:27,610 --> 00:07:28,650
Invite your wife too.

153
00:07:29,290 --> 00:07:30,320
I came up with some ideas.

154
00:07:30,410 --> 00:07:31,360
We can talk about it then.

155
00:07:32,210 --> 00:07:32,920
I'm so sorry.

156
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,730
I promise my parents

157
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,800
to go back for dinner.

158
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,850
Let's find another time then.

159
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,090
That works too.

160
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,320
Let's meet next time.

161
00:07:44,730 --> 00:07:46,560
You are running around these days.

162
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,770
Finally, we caught you.

163
00:07:48,170 --> 00:07:50,290
The investor fled, but I didn't.

164
00:07:50,410 --> 00:07:51,120
This is my home.

165
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,740
- When did I run away?
- We won't listen to that.

166
00:07:52,740 --> 00:07:54,020
Stop your lies.

167
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,050
How can you say that?

168
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:56,240
You forget what you agreed...?

169
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,120
What did we do?

170
00:07:57,170 --> 00:07:58,220
We believe you.

171
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,040
We believe you.
And this is what we got...

172
00:08:00,090 --> 00:08:00,850
No need to say more.

173
00:08:00,970 --> 00:08:02,200
Listen, pay up what you owe us.

174
00:08:02,210 --> 00:08:03,730
Are you still my friends?

175
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:05,440
Likes who cares. You better stop lying.

176
00:08:05,610 --> 00:08:07,120
We don't believe you, you know?

177
00:08:07,210 --> 00:08:08,680
We promised to make money together...

178
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,170
Xia Guo. Xia Guo is here.

179
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:11,620
What has happened, Madam Xu, Madam Li?

180
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,920
Xia Guo, it's good you are here.

181
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,480
Listen.

182
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,200
Your mother-in-law borrowed our money

183
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,360
for investment.

184
00:08:16,530 --> 00:08:17,860
That's right. She borrowed our money

185
00:08:17,860 --> 00:08:18,700
and didn't pay back.

186
00:08:18,770 --> 00:08:20,920
Should we demand the money from her?

187
00:08:21,050 --> 00:08:22,560
Why should I pay you the money?

188
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,320
- What's going on?
- Don't listen to them.

189
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,730
How much did she borrow?

190
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:27,680
It was 120,000.

191
00:08:27,770 --> 00:08:28,610
Xia Guo,

192
00:08:28,610 --> 00:08:30,530
this money means nothing to you.

193
00:08:30,530 --> 00:08:31,240
You are rich.

194
00:08:31,410 --> 00:08:33,010
- Help her pay up.
- That's right.

195
00:08:33,010 --> 00:08:34,020
- Why must she do that?
- Help her pay.

196
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:34,720
Unreasonable.

197
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,050
No friendship at all...

198
00:08:36,800 --> 00:08:38,560
Pay up!

199
00:08:39,130 --> 00:08:40,480
Pay up!

200
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:44,050
- Trying to run away?
- Pay up!

201
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,560
You can't run away.

202
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:48,480
Guo.

203
00:08:50,050 --> 00:08:51,410
Guo, does it hurt?

204
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,920
Let me see. Are you all right?

205
00:08:53,010 --> 00:08:53,960
I'm good.

206
00:08:54,650 --> 00:08:55,800
What are you doing?

207
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,890
How can you hit her?

208
00:08:57,170 --> 00:08:57,800
I didn't.

209
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,180
Did you see me hitting her?

210
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:00,050
- That's right.
- Listen.

211
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,250
- Stop talking.
- That's right.

212
00:09:01,370 --> 00:09:03,080
- Anyway, you owe us money.
- Pay back.

213
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:04,890
You signed the contract yourself.

214
00:09:05,130 --> 00:09:06,680
I also wasted more than 300,000.

215
00:09:06,890 --> 00:09:08,760
How could you demand money from me?

216
00:09:08,890 --> 00:09:10,770
Enough, stop already!

217
00:09:15,650 --> 00:09:16,770
Madam Li, Madam Xu.

218
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,840
You have been friends
with Mrs. Yu for years.

219
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:19,680
You know

220
00:09:19,770 --> 00:09:21,490
what of a person she is, right?

221
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,960
It was a good intention

222
00:09:23,050 --> 00:09:24,320
when she invited you to invest,

223
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,890
thinking you could make money together.

224
00:09:26,050 --> 00:09:26,770
Besides, I believe

225
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,920
she has analyzed

226
00:09:28,170 --> 00:09:29,440
both the benefits and risks to you

227
00:09:29,530 --> 00:09:31,250
before the investment, right?

228
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:32,530
It's risky for sure.

229
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,980
You can share the money if you get.

230
00:09:34,010 --> 00:09:34,660
If you lose money,

231
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:36,130
you should bear the risk together.

232
00:09:36,250 --> 00:09:37,370
She is also a victim.

233
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,720
No one wants to lose their money.

234
00:09:38,890 --> 00:09:39,650
If you keep like this,

235
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,010
we'll call the police.

236
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:42,560
If you say so,

237
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,900
fine, go and call the police.

238
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:45,220
The police'll arrest who?

239
00:09:45,290 --> 00:09:46,320
You guys, of course.

240
00:09:46,410 --> 00:09:47,200
You think I dared not?

241
00:09:47,290 --> 00:09:48,220
I'm calling the police now.

242
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:50,040
Let's see who will get arrested.

243
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,200
Do you own the police station?

244
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,440
- Calm down.
- Just pay up.

245
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:54,130
Enough.

246
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,800
We will pay the money

247
00:09:55,890 --> 00:09:57,040
we owe you.

248
00:09:57,130 --> 00:09:58,560
But you have to give us time

249
00:09:58,560 --> 00:09:59,530
to gather money, right?

250
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,720
Nonsense, Guo.

251
00:10:01,170 --> 00:10:02,170
At least pay us half.

252
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,250
- Right. Half.
- No more haggling.

253
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,440
I have no money.

254
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,920
You keep saying that.

255
00:10:06,010 --> 00:10:07,000
That's right.

256
00:10:07,050 --> 00:10:08,050
You can't have it your way.

257
00:10:08,130 --> 00:10:08,720
Madam Li.

258
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:09,860
Come. Let's talk.

259
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,530
What?

260
00:10:10,650 --> 00:10:11,680
Come here.

261
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,490
Guo.

262
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:14,600
What are you going to tell her?

263
00:10:22,130 --> 00:10:22,890
All right?

264
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:25,890
Fine.

265
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,370
That's it for this.

266
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:29,680
Hurry and gather the money

267
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,600
to pay us back, okay?

268
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,720
- Okay.
- Wait. What was it?

269
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,650
Tell you later.

270
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,170
That's it for today.

271
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,680
Everyone, leave.

272
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,370
Just leave.

273
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,770
- Let's leave.
- Why are we leaving?

274
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,560
Did she talk to you

275
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,800
and fool you?

276
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,800
Let's go.

277
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,530
It's all right, Mrs. Yu.

278
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:47,080
- It's all right. Let's go home.
- What did you tell them?

279
00:10:47,170 --> 00:10:47,840
Let's go home.

280
00:10:48,130 --> 00:10:49,680
It's nothing here. Please leave.

281
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,560
- Please leave.
- Come on.

282
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,530
Guo,

283
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,490
what's wrong?

284
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,960
- Are you all right?
- Are you good?

