Don't abort the child.

577
00:23:43,120 --> 00:23:44,690
Just wait up.

578
00:23:46,560 --> 00:23:47,450
You brat.

579
00:23:47,690 --> 00:23:49,050
I'm so furious.

580
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:50,600
Mom.

581
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:52,840
Mom, sit down.

582
00:23:56,080 --> 00:23:57,210
Mom, calm down.

583
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:58,690
With the issues in our family,

584
00:23:58,770 --> 00:24:00,290
it's not appropriate
to have a child now.

585
00:24:00,640 --> 00:24:02,800
Nonsense.

586
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:04,560
When we had you

587
00:24:04,690 --> 00:24:05,640
and Yan,

588
00:24:05,730 --> 00:24:08,050
things were tougher than now.

589
00:24:09,010 --> 00:24:10,250
But the situation

590
00:24:10,360 --> 00:24:12,690
is different now.

591
00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:14,490
I didn't marry Guo

592
00:24:14,560 --> 00:24:15,160
for her

593
00:24:15,250 --> 00:24:16,530
to bear my child.

594
00:24:16,840 --> 00:24:17,690
The situation now

595
00:24:17,770 --> 00:24:18,970
is she doesn't want a child.

596
00:24:19,250 --> 00:24:20,120
She wants to work.

597
00:24:20,250 --> 00:24:21,930
I can't influence her future, can I?

598
00:24:22,450 --> 00:24:23,770
Just use your brain

599
00:24:23,840 --> 00:24:25,360
and think carefully.

600
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:27,080
Had Guo not wanted the child,

601
00:24:27,210 --> 00:24:28,290
she could have done that.

602
00:24:28,770 --> 00:24:30,560
Why must she discuss it with you?

603
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:34,460
She discussed it with you

604
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:36,210
because she still had hope.

605
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,640
Since the child has come to us,

606
00:24:37,930 --> 00:24:38,800
that means we are fated.

607
00:24:38,930 --> 00:24:39,800
How could you

608
00:24:39,930 --> 00:24:41,400
abandon the child?

609
00:24:41,730 --> 00:24:42,320
Still sitting?

610
00:24:42,450 --> 00:24:44,010
Go and get her back.

611
00:24:45,770 --> 00:24:47,120
Now!

612
00:24:47,250 --> 00:24:48,360
If you can't get Guo

613
00:24:48,690 --> 00:24:49,770
and the child back,

614
00:24:50,080 --> 00:24:51,690
don't come back.

615
00:25:12,530 --> 00:25:14,690
Sir, please drive faster.

616
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:45,300
(Leshan Maternity and Infant Hospital)

617
00:26:02,770 --> 00:26:03,880
Sorry, Guo.

618
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:05,800
I'm late.

619
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:08,530
Dear.

620
00:26:09,450 --> 00:26:10,840
I will give you a wedding

621
00:26:11,970 --> 00:26:14,050
and give your mom the dowry.

622
00:26:14,560 --> 00:26:15,840
We can have another child later.

623
00:26:17,840 --> 00:26:18,840
I won't put you

624
00:26:18,840 --> 00:26:19,970
through this ever again.

625
00:26:20,770 --> 00:26:22,080
Does it hurt very much?

626
00:26:26,490 --> 00:26:28,160
Come. I will carry you home.

627
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,640
You are smooshing the child.

628
00:26:36,640 --> 00:26:37,560
Put me down.

629
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:39,490
The baby is with me.

630
00:26:40,080 --> 00:26:41,160
What?

631
00:26:42,080 --> 00:26:43,160
You kept the child?

632
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:48,600
I couldn't bear to abort it.

633
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:04,210
That's wonderful.

634
00:27:05,250 --> 00:27:07,250
You kept the child.

635
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:11,930
I'm a father now.

636
00:27:16,160 --> 00:27:18,120
I'm a father now.

637
00:27:21,600 --> 00:27:22,560
Promise me,

638
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:23,970
Drop the lease

639
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,010
and save all the money

640
00:27:25,010 --> 00:27:26,290
for our child,

641
00:27:26,970 --> 00:27:27,840
all right?

642
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:32,290
Yes, I will do what you say from now on.

643
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:35,770
Everything you say.

644
00:27:43,250 --> 00:27:45,010
(The life inside me)

645
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:47,010
(is my weak spot)

646
00:27:47,600 --> 00:27:49,120
(and also my armor.)

647
00:27:50,250 --> 00:27:51,880
(It makes me more resolute)

648
00:27:52,250 --> 00:27:53,970
(about my decision to stay.)

649
00:27:55,010 --> 00:27:56,800
(Striving for the common goal)

650
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,600
(and none of us give up.)

651
00:27:59,730 --> 00:28:00,800
(Perhaps)

652
00:28:01,450 --> 00:28:03,250
(this is what family means.)

653
00:28:04,320 --> 00:28:05,290
Slowly.

654
00:28:05,770 --> 00:28:06,800
Slowly.

655
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:09,970
Please have a look. This is all.

656
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:11,360
Please sign it.

657
00:28:11,560 --> 00:28:12,640
Okay. Here?

658
00:28:12,770 --> 00:28:13,970
Yes.

659
00:28:16,050 --> 00:28:16,800
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

660
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,930
Contact us next time.

661
00:28:28,080 --> 00:28:29,840
When I first rented this apartment,

662
00:28:31,360 --> 00:28:32,530
I thought about

663
00:28:32,690 --> 00:28:34,530
showing you the most beautiful sunset.

664
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:37,160
Unexpectedly,

665
00:28:38,210 --> 00:28:39,690
we are moving out so soon.

666
00:28:46,290 --> 00:28:48,450
It's not sunny every day.

667
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:50,730
Most of the time,

668
00:28:50,730 --> 00:28:52,730
we don't have time to see the sunset.

669
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,970
So, don't hold on to that.

670
00:28:56,250 --> 00:28:57,400
You don't have to console me.

671
00:28:59,050 --> 00:29:00,080
Making you happy

672
00:29:00,560 --> 00:29:01,730
is something I hold on to.

673
00:29:01,930 --> 00:29:02,730
You gave up the chance

674
00:29:03,010 --> 00:29:04,160
to Shanghai and look after Dad

675
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,300
because of me.

676
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:07,250
Well, let's get this over.

677
00:29:08,560 --> 00:29:10,010
This is my choice.

678
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:12,320
I don't need you to sacrifice
or repay me anything.

679
00:29:13,160 --> 00:29:14,400
That's not what I mean.

680
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:21,290
When I was in the operating room
that day,

681
00:29:22,120 --> 00:29:23,560
I was really scared.

682
00:29:24,450 --> 00:29:25,690
I felt upset,

683
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:27,930
even regretted it.

684
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:30,970
I hated you for not coming to stop me.

685
00:29:33,210 --> 00:29:34,210
But when I saw you

686
00:29:34,210 --> 00:29:35,730
in the hallway,

687
00:29:37,730 --> 00:29:38,970
I felt reassured.

688
00:29:40,290 --> 00:29:41,930
I knew you were by my side.

689
00:29:43,080 --> 00:29:45,970
I could trust and rely on you.

690
00:29:49,690 --> 00:29:50,600
Yu Jian,

691
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:52,970
with you around,

692
00:29:53,490 --> 00:29:55,640
we can overcome all the difficulties.

693
00:29:59,220 --> 00:30:00,690
(Marriage Certificate)

694
00:30:00,690 --> 00:30:01,560
Guo,

695
00:30:01,970 --> 00:30:03,730
today is the day
we register for marriage.

696
00:30:05,120 --> 00:30:06,320
I swear

697
00:30:06,970 --> 00:30:08,080
on the marriage certificate

698
00:30:08,490 --> 00:30:09,400
that I will

699
00:30:10,320 --> 00:30:11,450
give you a bigger

700
00:30:11,450 --> 00:30:13,050
and finer house in the future.

701
00:30:13,770 --> 00:30:15,010
I will give you

702
00:30:15,770 --> 00:30:17,210
the grandest wedding.

703
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,050
If I can't do that,

704
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:21,210
I will...

705
00:30:21,210 --> 00:30:21,970
What?

706
00:30:21,970 --> 00:30:23,600
Bet your life?

707
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:39,880
(Tang Yiming: 30,000 yuan to you)
Take it. I wish you double happiness.

708
00:30:40,250 --> 00:30:40,970
After child is born,

709
00:30:41,290 --> 00:30:42,450
I'll be the godfather.

710
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:48,320
Tang, you sent me money?

711
00:30:49,450 --> 00:30:50,250
Not only me,

712
00:30:50,560 --> 00:30:51,560
a few from our alumni group

713
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:52,290
chipped in

714
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:53,080
after knowing this.

715
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,210
Take it.

716
00:30:54,490 --> 00:30:55,320
I can't.

717
00:30:55,500 --> 00:30:57,630
Don't overthink. It's not for you,

718
00:30:57,930 --> 00:30:58,730
it's for your child.

719
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:00,530
Keep it for your child.

720
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:01,970
No, it isn't appropriate.

721
00:31:02,290 --> 00:31:03,770
Cut that out.
We are friends, aren't we?

722
00:31:04,930 --> 00:31:06,010
Hurry up and settle the things

723
00:31:06,010 --> 00:31:06,770
and come to work.

724
00:31:07,010 --> 00:31:07,970
We have more projects now.

725
00:31:07,970 --> 00:31:08,880
It's going to be busy.

726
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:11,050
By the way,
don't forget the wedding banquet.

727
00:31:11,690 --> 00:31:12,970
All right.

728
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,210
Tang...

729
00:31:17,250 --> 00:31:18,360
He's insane.

730
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:20,840
It's our luck to have friends like him.

731
00:31:24,010 --> 00:31:25,730
(Wen)
Double happiness. Be happy.

732
00:31:25,730 --> 00:31:27,560
(Guan)
Leader, this is for your child.

733
00:31:27,930 --> 00:31:29,530
- Please keep it.
- Congratulations, Yu Jian.

734
00:31:29,530 --> 00:31:31,360
(Yang)
We're waiting for the wedding banquet.

735
00:31:36,940 --> 00:31:40,620
♪The laid-back lights in the city...♪

736
00:31:40,640 --> 00:31:42,770
(Wen Ya)
Yu Jian, I paid the design fee early.

737
00:31:43,050 --> 00:31:44,800
(100,000 yuan arrived)
Keep up the good work.

738
00:31:45,250 --> 00:31:46,080
Congratulations.

739
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:51,120
Hello?

740
00:31:51,450 --> 00:31:52,210
Hello, Xia Guo.

741
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:54,450
This is Shuangli Trading.

742
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:56,120
I have discuss

743
00:31:56,210 --> 00:31:57,360
with the superior.

744
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:58,210
We decided

745
00:31:58,320 --> 00:31:59,690
to hire you as planned.

746
00:31:59,970 --> 00:32:00,880
Really?

747
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:02,970
You work so hard when you are pregnant.

748
00:32:03,050 --> 00:32:04,320
The superior expects your work.

749
00:32:05,290 --> 00:32:06,400
Seize the opportunity.

750
00:32:06,600 --> 00:32:07,400
Work harder.

751
00:32:07,560 --> 00:32:08,930
Sure, I will.

752
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:10,250
Please come

753
00:32:10,320 --> 00:32:11,560
to sign the contract next Monday.

754
00:32:11,730 --> 00:32:12,250
We will

755
00:32:12,360 --> 00:32:13,400
discuss your job scope

756
00:32:13,530 --> 00:32:14,530
in more detail.

757
00:32:14,970 --> 00:32:15,840
Yes, sure.

758
00:32:16,120 --> 00:32:17,160
I will be there on time.

759
00:32:17,970 --> 00:32:19,010
Thank you.

760
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:20,800
What's wrong?

761
00:32:21,730 --> 00:32:22,970
I got the job.

762
00:32:28,050 --> 00:32:29,010
Guo,

763
00:32:29,770 --> 00:32:31,800
we will be very happy

764
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:33,400
and lead a good life.

765
00:32:34,980 --> 00:32:38,620
♪Our life amidst the gale...♪

766
00:32:38,970 --> 00:32:40,600
(Wedding Vow)
Look at this.

767
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,840
How did you take it?

768
00:32:45,250 --> 00:32:46,210
Everyone reads the vow

769
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:49,010
when they register for marriage.

770
00:32:49,360 --> 00:32:50,490
So I took it.

771
00:32:52,210 --> 00:32:54,050
Let's make up for it.

772
00:32:55,970 --> 00:32:57,080
I, Yu Jian.

773
00:32:57,360 --> 00:32:58,600
I, Xia Guo.

774
00:32:58,770 --> 00:33:01,120
We voluntarily become husband and wife.

775
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:02,560
Starting today.

776
00:33:02,690 --> 00:33:03,800
Starting today.

777
00:33:03,970 --> 00:33:05,010
Starting today,

778
00:33:05,250 --> 00:33:06,930
we will shoulder

779
00:33:07,010 --> 00:33:09,640
the responsibility and duty
of marriage together.

780
00:33:09,930 --> 00:33:11,490
Look, let's respond to the national call

781
00:33:11,970 --> 00:33:13,010
and have two children.

782
00:33:13,320 --> 00:33:14,360
When we grow old,

783
00:33:14,360 --> 00:33:15,560
we will have grandchildren.

784
00:33:15,770 --> 00:33:17,250
(Isn't it wonderful)

785
00:33:17,250 --> 00:33:18,050
(to have all of them)

786
00:33:18,400 --> 00:33:19,360
(waiting on us?)

787
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,930
(Guo.)

788
00:33:22,930 --> 00:33:23,620
(Marry Me)

789
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:25,970
(Let's get married.)

790
00:33:27,010 --> 00:33:28,600
(I can't wait any longer.)

791
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:32,050
(From this day forward,
for better or for worse,)

792
00:33:32,490 --> 00:33:34,400
(for richer or for poorer,)

793
00:33:34,930 --> 00:33:36,770
(in sickness or in health,)

794
00:33:37,210 --> 00:33:39,210
(young or old,)

795
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:42,530
(we will endure hardships)

796
00:33:42,770 --> 00:33:43,880
(and share joy and sorrows.)

797
00:33:44,210 --> 00:33:46,120
(We are lifelong partners
to each other.)

798
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:48,640
(We will uphold our vows made today.)

799
00:33:49,250 --> 00:33:52,770
(We will firmly uphold our vows
made today.)

800
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:05,400
Thanks.

801
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,120
Mr. Wang.

802
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:08,200
Miss Xia,

803
00:34:08,410 --> 00:34:09,720
I'm in your room.

804
00:34:10,050 --> 00:34:11,200
It's raining hard today.

805
00:34:11,720 --> 00:34:13,530
The windows were blown open,

806
00:34:13,530 --> 00:34:14,890
and the room is flooded.

807
00:34:14,890 --> 00:34:16,330
It's leaking to the floor below.

808
00:34:16,450 --> 00:34:18,050
I have reached the entrance
of the alley.

809
00:34:18,050 --> 00:34:19,410
I will be there soon.

810
00:34:26,640 --> 00:34:27,640
Mr. Wang.

811
00:34:28,080 --> 00:34:30,080
Xia, you are finally back.

812
00:34:39,640 --> 00:34:40,640
Mr. Wang, thank you so much

813
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,890
for helping me.

814
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:45,010
This place hasn't been repaired
for years.

815
00:34:45,560 --> 00:34:47,080
Look, the window blew open,

816
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:48,050
and the walls cracked.

817
00:34:48,410 --> 00:34:50,600
The property management promised
to repair all the houses,

818
00:34:50,720 --> 00:34:51,760
but they did nothing.

819
00:34:52,680 --> 00:34:53,560
The rain is heavy today.

820
00:34:53,720 --> 00:34:55,010
You can't stay here.

821
00:34:55,530 --> 00:34:56,530
Don't worry, Mr. Wang.

822
00:34:56,720 --> 00:34:57,810
I will find a hotel

823
00:34:57,890 --> 00:34:59,010
and manage one night.

824
00:34:59,640 --> 00:35:00,890
One night isn't enough.

825
00:35:01,410 --> 00:35:02,600
The weather broadcast says

826
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:04,530
this rain will continue
for at least two days.

827
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:08,370
Xia, sorry about this.

828
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:09,160
I don't want

829
00:35:09,240 --> 00:35:11,010
to rent this place for now.

830
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,160
Sorry?

831
00:35:14,330 --> 00:35:16,280
You paid the rent for six months,

832
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:17,330
and it has been five months.

833
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:19,080
I'll only take rents for three months.

834
00:35:19,970 --> 00:35:20,760
Wait, Mr. Wang.

835
00:35:20,850 --> 00:35:22,560
I have many things here.

836
00:35:22,810 --> 00:35:23,930
Don't worry.

837
00:35:24,010 --> 00:35:25,680
You can get them
once you find another place.

838
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:36,530
(Xue Yuming: Have you reached home yet?)

839
00:35:41,640 --> 00:35:42,720
(Xia Guo: Yes.)

840
00:35:59,900 --> 00:36:03,420
(Peak hours, waiting for a cab)

841
00:36:24,640 --> 00:36:26,120
It's a downpour. Why still come here?

842
00:36:26,530 --> 00:36:27,530
What's wrong with you?

843
00:36:28,450 --> 00:36:29,120
It's not that.

844
00:36:29,200 --> 00:36:30,600
The place I rent is leaking.

845
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:31,490
I can't stay there.

846
00:36:31,720 --> 00:36:33,450
I wanted to find a hotel
but there's no cab.

847
00:36:34,160 --> 00:36:35,240
So I came here for shelter.

848
00:36:36,490 --> 00:36:38,640
The houses across are a bit run-down.

849
00:36:40,330 --> 00:36:41,490
I rent a place in Shanghai too.

850
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:42,810
I'm quite close with the agents.

851
00:36:42,970 --> 00:36:44,050
I could ask around for you.

852
00:36:44,930 --> 00:36:46,370
Sure. If you feel it's convenient,

853
00:36:46,450 --> 00:36:47,120
help me.

854
00:36:47,370 --> 00:36:47,890
Thanks.

855
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:48,890
No problem.

856
00:36:49,410 --> 00:36:50,120
Here you go.

857
00:36:51,370 --> 00:36:52,530
Thanks.

858
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:02,010
Wrong taste?

859
00:37:02,120 --> 00:37:03,410
The taste doesn't change,

860
00:37:05,160 --> 00:37:06,330
maybe I have changed.

861
00:37:15,160 --> 00:37:17,120
It's rude
that you stare at me like that.

862
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:18,970
I just want to observe
